Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:54.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}進むことに飽きたの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:57.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}叶えても　叶うだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:01:02.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢はなぜこの手で　形を変えてくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:08.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}教えて　どれくらい？　頑張れば辿り着くの…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:14.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}理想につぶれてた　私はもういない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:17.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先をリライト
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:20.73,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}掴みたいよ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:28.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君と声を重ねて　届けるの　もっと先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:31.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ歩けない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:34.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}景色　君とみてみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:37.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ進めない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直感を信じて生きてたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:43.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先の New World
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:46.63,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}聞こえていますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:50.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}この声が終わるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:54.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君に伝え続けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:28.80,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重寫夢想的續集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:32.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}會聽到未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:37.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我們的聲音重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:46.32,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}送出的開場曲 飛向夢想吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:51.45,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}總是尋找平坦的路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:54.74,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}只會讓我厭倦前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:57.75,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}就算去實現 也只是完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:01:02.71,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢想為何會因為這隻手改變形態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:08.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}請告訴我 還要努力多久才能到達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:14.05,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}曾經只能仰視理想的我 已經改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:17.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重寫夢想的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:20.73,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望把握住未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:28.11,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我們的聲音重疊 直抵更遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:31.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一個人走不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:34.37,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}想和你一同欣賞美景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:37.66,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一個人無法前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.29,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望能追隨直覺活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:43.37,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢想前方的新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:46.63,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}你聽清楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:50.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直到無法發聲為止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:54.43,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我都會一直為你開口
Comment: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:08.22,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,---------------------------ED「STAND BY YOU」------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:13.61,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by me, you did that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:16.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:26.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}気持ち伝えるのにいつも何故　こんなにも悩み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:29.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ゆらり揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:36.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}本当は君が好きなのに　うらはらで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:39.76,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}上手く言えないよ　ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:42.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}振り返れば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.93,0:22:45.64,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}君が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:49.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}目と目合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:54.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}愛の歌　そう唄い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.48,0:23:00.69,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}君にいつか届くまでね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:03.28,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}大事にしてたフィーリング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:05.74,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全部込めるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:10.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ちゃんと受け止めてくれるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:16.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}真夜中のラブソングで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:21.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}世界がちょっと変わってほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:27.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}そして君とsweetie　2人ぼっち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:30.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}100ミリちょっとの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:32.10,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}隙間埋める
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:33.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}be with you
Comment: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:13.61,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by me, you did that
Comment: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:16.23,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:26.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}只是表明心意 為什麼讓我如此煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:29.33,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}總是搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:36.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}其實那麼喜歡你 卻言不由衷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:39.76,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}找不到合適的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:42.47,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}回首身後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.93,0:22:45.64,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}眼中有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:49.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}我們四目相對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:54.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}唱響這首愛之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.48,0:23:00.69,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}希望有一天你能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:03.28,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}一直珍惜的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:05.74,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}都包含其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:10.75,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}你一定會接受它吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:16.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}願這首午夜小情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:21.97,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}可以讓世界稍微改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:27.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}然後與你甜甜蜜蜜 二人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:30.01,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}十多公分的間隙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:32.10,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全都被填滿
Comment: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:33.94,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,be with you
